<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Disaster Management System</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    nav {
      background-color: #2f3542;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/images/disaster-bg.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      padding: 8rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #1e90ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }
    
    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #1873cc;
    }
    
    .features {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: white;
    }
    
    .features h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #2f3542;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .feature-item {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #1e90ff;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .feature-item h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2f3542;
    }
    
    .recent-disasters {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
    }
    
    .recent-disasters h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #2f3542;
    }
    
    .disasters-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .disaster-card {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    
    .disaster-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    
    .disaster-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .disaster-content h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
    
    .disaster-content p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #666;
    }
    
    .disaster-status {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .status-pending {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      color: #856404;
    }
    
    .status-critical {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
    }
    
    .status-resolved {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
    }
    
    .view-more {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    
    .view-more a {
      color: #1e90ff;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    footer {
      background-color: #2f3542;
      color: white;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      
      .hero p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/reports">Reports</a>
    <a href="/media">Media</a>
    <a href="/livemap">Live Map</a>
    <% if(currentUser && currentUser.userType === 'donor') { %>
      <a href="/donor/dashboard">My Dashboard</a>
    <% } else if(currentUser && currentUser.userType === 'admin') { %>
      <a href="/admin">Admin</a>
    <% } %>
    <span style="margin-left: auto; color: white;">
      <% if(currentUser) { %>
        Welcome, <%= currentUser.name || currentUser.username %> |
        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
      <% } %>
    </span>
  </nav>
  
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Disaster Management System</h1>
    <p>Help communities recover from disasters by providing real-time reports, tracking resources, and facilitating donations.</p>
    <a href="/reports" class="cta-button">View Reports</a>
  </section>
  
  <section class="features">
    <h2>How Our Platform Works</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">üìù</div>
        <h3>Report Disasters</h3>
        <p>Submit detailed reports about disasters with location information and resource requirements.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">üó∫Ô∏è</div>
        <h3>Live Map</h3>
        <p>View disaster locations on an interactive map to understand affected areas and coordinate response efforts.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">ü§ù</div>
        <h3>Donate Resources</h3>
        <p>Easily donate required resources to help affected communities recover faster.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="recent-disasters">
    <h2>Recent Disasters</h2>
    <div class="disasters-grid">
      <!-- This will be populated by server with recent reports -->
      <div class="disaster-card">
        <img src="/uploads/placeholder.jpg" alt="Disaster Image">
        <div class="disaster-content">
          <span class="disaster-status status-critical">Critical</span>
          <h3>Flood in Mumbai</h3>
          <p>Heavy rainfall has caused flooding in several areas of Mumbai, affecting thousands of residents.</p>
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> April 18, 2025</p>
          <a href="/reports" style="color: #1e90ff; font-weight: 600;">View Details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="disaster-card">
        <img src="/uploads/placeholder.jpg" alt="Disaster Image">
        <div class="disaster-content">
          <span class="disaster-status status-pending">Pending</span>
          <h3>Earthquake in Delhi</h3>
          <p>A 5.8 magnitude earthquake has affected parts of Delhi and surrounding areas.</p>
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> April 15, 2025</p>
          <a href="/reports" style="color: #1e90ff; font-weight: 600;">View Details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="disaster-card">
        <img src="/uploads/placeholder.jpg" alt="Disaster Image">
        <div class="disaster-content">
          <span class="disaster-status status-resolved">Resolved</span>
          <h3>Cyclone in Chennai</h3>
          <p>Cyclone has been successfully managed with minimal damage to property and no casualties.</p>
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> April 10, 2025</p>
          <a href="/reports" style="color: #1e90ff; font-weight: 600;">View Details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="view-more">
      <a href="/reports">View All Reports ‚Üí</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Disaster Management System | Developed by <%= currentUser ? currentUser.name || currentUser.username : 'muhammadparkar' %></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>